WEBVTT

00:08.967 --> 00:13.388
<i>[Bill Martin &amp; Phil Coulter's "I Gotta Get</i>
<i>the World Off My Back" plays on radio]</i>

00:20.729 --> 00:22.105
<i>[manager] You need to get out. </i>

00:22.522 --> 00:24.399
<i>You smell,</i>
<i>and you're frightening my clientele.</i>

00:24.482 --> 00:25.692
<i>-I told you--</i>
<i>-How dare you?</i>

00:25.775 --> 00:27.610
<i>I am a member of the royal family.</i>

00:27.694 --> 00:29.779
<i>-[Klaus grunts]</i>
<i>-[manager] You are not a member of...</i>

00:29.863 --> 00:30.989
<i>[grunting] ...the royal...</i>

00:31.072 --> 00:33.783
<i>-He's touching me inappropriately!</i>
<i>-I told you once, I told you twice!</i>

00:33.867 --> 00:34.868
<i>-Get out!</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

00:34.951 --> 00:37.620
<i>[manager] Don't come back</i>
<i>till you can pay your damn bill!</i>

00:38.621 --> 00:40.206
<i>-Chanel.</i>
<i>-[woman gasps]</i>

00:40.290 --> 00:42.709
<i>Oh, you poor thing.</i>

00:43.084 --> 00:45.086
<i>Let me help you up.</i>

00:47.839 --> 00:49.799
<i>Oh! Oh!</i>

00:49.883 --> 00:51.342
<i>[whimpers] Thank you. </i>

00:51.426 --> 00:52.886
<i>Come with me. </i>

00:53.428 --> 00:54.304
<i>[Klaus] Okay.</i>

00:54.721 --> 00:57.599
<i>-[woman] I'll take care of you.</i>
<i>-[Ben] Seriously, Klaus?</i>

00:57.682 --> 01:00.518
<i>-[Boney M.'s "Sunny" plays]</i>
-♪ Sunny ♪

01:01.895 --> 01:05.482
<i>♪ Yesterday my life was filled with rain ♪</i>

01:06.733 --> 01:08.026
<i>♪ Sunny ♪</i>

01:09.569 --> 01:13.448
<i>♪ You smile at me</i>
<i>And really ease the pain ♪</i>

01:13.865 --> 01:16.367
<i>-[gasps, murmurs of amazement]</i>
-♪ The dark days are gone ♪

01:16.451 --> 01:18.286
<i>♪ The bright days are here ♪</i>

01:18.411 --> 01:22.332
<i>♪ My sunny one shines so sincere ♪</i>

01:22.415 --> 01:25.126
<i>-♪ Sunny, one so true ♪</i>
<i>-</i>Thank you.

01:25.543 --> 01:29.923
<i>♪ I love you ♪</i>

01:30.465 --> 01:31.758
<i>-</i>♪ Sunny ♪
<i>-[grunts softly]</i>

01:31.841 --> 01:33.093
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

01:33.384 --> 01:37.013
<i>♪ Thank you for the sunshine bouquet ♪</i>

01:37.097 --> 01:39.099
<i>-♪ That sweet bouquet, Sunny ♪</i>
-[grunting]

01:39.182 --> 01:40.391
<i>-Okay.</i>
<i>-[groans]</i>

01:40.475 --> 01:41.392
<i>[grunts heavily]</i>

01:41.476 --> 01:44.729
<i>♪ Thank you for the love</i>
<i>You brought my way ♪</i>

01:44.813 --> 01:45.855
<i>[laughs]</i>

01:46.106 --> 01:49.567
<i>♪ You gave to me your all and all ♪</i>

01:49.651 --> 01:53.571
<i>♪ And now I feel ten feet tall ♪</i>

01:54.155 --> 01:57.033
<i>♪ Sunny, one so true ♪</i>

01:57.117 --> 02:01.746
<i>♪ I love you ♪</i>

02:01.830 --> 02:03.873
<i>♪ Sunny ♪</i>

02:04.999 --> 02:08.586
<i>♪ Thank you for the truth you let me see ♪</i>

02:09.879 --> 02:11.339
<i>♪ Sunny ♪</i>

02:11.631 --> 02:13.007
<i>[man] Everybody, duck!</i>

02:13.091 --> 02:16.469
<i>♪ Thank you for the facts from A to Z ♪</i>

02:17.512 --> 02:21.057
<i>♪ My life was torn like windblown sand ♪</i>

02:21.141 --> 02:25.103
<i>♪ And the rock was formed</i>
<i>When you held my hand ♪</i>

02:25.186 --> 02:28.523
<i>-[followers crooning]</i>
-♪ Sunny, one so true ♪

02:28.606 --> 02:32.318
<i>-♪ I love you ♪</i>
-[overlapping murmurs]

02:33.361 --> 02:35.029
<i>♪ Sunny ♪</i>

02:37.574 --> 02:39.993
<i>-[followers murmuring]</i>
<i>-Now, steady. Hands off!</i>

02:40.535 --> 02:42.162
<i>Just let go... Just...</i>

02:42.537 --> 02:43.621
<i>form an orderly...</i>

02:44.455 --> 02:46.457
<i>[followers moaning, murmuring]</i>

02:48.251 --> 02:49.836
<i>Destiny's Children!</i>

02:49.919 --> 02:51.296
<i>[crowd gasping]</i>

02:51.379 --> 02:54.883
<i>[Klaus] Let us all commune with music.</i>

02:58.136 --> 02:59.804
<i>[whistles single note]</i>

02:59.888 --> 03:02.223
<i>[all whistling]</i>

03:03.641 --> 03:04.893
<i>[whistling continues]</i>

03:04.976 --> 03:06.644
<i>♪ Sunny... ♪</i>

03:08.605 --> 03:10.106
<i>-[Klaus] Get in the car. </i>
<i>-What? Why?</i>

03:10.190 --> 03:11.649
<i>-Where are we going?</i>
<i>-[Klaus] Away.</i>

03:11.900 --> 03:14.277
<i>-Hurry. Quick, quick, quick, quick.</i>
<i>-[Ben] Away where?</i>

03:14.569 --> 03:17.614
<i>-[Klaus sighs] To see an old friend.</i>
<i>-[Ben] You can't just run out on them.</i>

03:17.697 --> 03:18.907
<i>[Klaus] Yeah, watch me.</i>

03:20.783 --> 03:23.494
<i>♪ Sunny, one so true ♪</i>

03:23.828 --> 03:27.457
<i>-♪ I love you ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Yeah ♪</i>

03:27.790 --> 03:29.959
<i>♪ I love you ♪</i>

03:30.043 --> 03:31.711
<i>♪ Yeah, my baby ♪</i>

03:31.794 --> 03:34.547
<i>-♪ I love you ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Sunny... </i>♪ [fading]

03:34.631 --> 03:36.132
<i>-[sizzling]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

03:36.216 --> 03:40.470
<i>-[screams]</i>
<i>-[Lila] Shh!</i>

03:40.553 --> 03:43.097
<i>Don't move. This thing is very finicky.</i>

03:45.975 --> 03:47.101
<i>[Diego] What happened?</i>

03:47.477 --> 03:49.437
<i>I saved your stupid life.</i>

03:49.938 --> 03:51.189
<i>Were you following me?</i>

03:51.606 --> 03:54.359
<i>Uh, hey, how about a little gratitude,</i>
<i>knife boy.</i>

03:54.651 --> 03:56.653
<i>If it wasn't for me, you'd be dead.</i>

03:57.320 --> 03:59.656
<i>-That's twice now, by the way.</i>
<i>-[metallic clink]</i>

04:00.365 --> 04:01.199
<i>Where are my clothes?</i>

04:01.282 --> 04:02.700
<i>The hell happened to my clothes?</i>

04:02.784 --> 04:04.786
<i>I said, don't move!</i>

04:04.869 --> 04:08.623
<i>-[sizzling]</i>
<i>-[shrieks, groaning]</i>

04:09.374 --> 04:10.500
<i>[soft moan]</i>

04:10.583 --> 04:12.043
<i>There. That's better.</i>

04:12.126 --> 04:13.169
<i>[energy whooshes]</i>

04:13.253 --> 04:14.295
<i>[Five sighs]</i>

04:14.921 --> 04:16.673
<i>Oh. He isn't dead.</i>

04:17.173 --> 04:19.717
<i>-[Lila] Disappointed?</i>
<i>-Oh, to see you? Always.</i>

04:21.219 --> 04:23.304
<i>So much hostility in such a tiny package.</i>

04:24.097 --> 04:25.640
<i>Did you cut yourself shaving?</i>

04:25.723 --> 04:27.642
<i>I could teach you to shave</i>
<i>like a big boy.</i>

04:27.976 --> 04:31.062
<i>[sighs]</i>
<i>No, I just ran into an old family friend.</i>

04:32.188 --> 04:34.899
<i>[soft snoring]</i>

04:38.152 --> 04:39.279
<i>You didn't untie him?</i>

04:40.989 --> 04:42.031
<i>Was I supposed to?</i>

04:42.407 --> 04:46.369
<i>["I Don't Care What They Say About You"</i>
<i>plays over radio]</i>

04:49.205 --> 04:54.669
<i>♪ I don't care what they say about you ♪</i>

04:55.753 --> 05:00.967
<i>♪ You're my darling, and I love you true ♪</i>

05:02.468 --> 05:08.391
<i>♪ All the things that happened</i>
<i>In the past ♪</i>

05:08.933 --> 05:14.355
<i>♪ Are forgotten</i>
<i>And you're mine at last... ♪</i>

05:15.773 --> 05:17.734
<i>[song continues indistinctly]</i>

05:21.863 --> 05:24.824
<i>-[song fading]</i>
<i>-[suspenseful instrumental music plays]</i>

05:47.430 --> 05:48.806
<i>[bushes rustling]</i>

05:49.599 --> 05:52.018
<i>-[tires screeching]</i>
<i>-[machine-gun fire, bullets ricocheting]</i>

05:53.311 --> 05:54.354
<i>[cries out]</i>

05:54.812 --> 05:57.065
<i>-[machine-gun fire continues]</i>
<i>-[Vanya gasping]</i>

05:57.523 --> 05:58.524
<i>[glass shatters]</i>

05:59.067 --> 06:00.193
<i>[engine sputtering]</i>

06:01.277 --> 06:04.572
<i>[engine stalling]</i>

06:05.198 --> 06:07.492
<i>-[gasping, panting]</i>
<i>-[keys jingling]</i>

06:25.051 --> 06:27.053
<i>[Vanya panting]</i>

06:30.848 --> 06:33.142
<i>-[bugs chirring]</i>
<i>-[slow, steady footsteps]</i>

06:41.234 --> 06:42.527
<i>[loud rustling]</i>

06:43.778 --> 06:45.488
<i>[running footsteps]</i>

06:49.909 --> 06:52.036
<i>[overlapping gunshots]</i>

06:55.456 --> 06:56.999
<i>[bullets whizzing by]</i>

07:04.924 --> 07:06.426
<i>[Vanya gasps, grunts]</i>

07:06.509 --> 07:07.969
<i>[bullets hitting cornstalks]</i>

07:10.555 --> 07:12.932
<i>-[gunfire continues]</i>
<i>-[gasping]</i>

07:18.146 --> 07:19.981
<i>[slo-mo boom]</i>

07:20.064 --> 07:22.066
<i>[high-pitched shattering]</i>

07:23.151 --> 07:25.069
<i>[percussive whoosh]</i>

07:38.249 --> 07:40.251
<i>[sign buzzing]</i>

07:43.713 --> 07:46.132
<i>[muted chatter</i>
<i>over police radio frequency]</i>

07:46.924 --> 07:48.968
<i>[alarm buzzing]</i>

07:49.051 --> 07:50.261
<i>Hey, we got one.</i>

07:51.220 --> 07:53.848
<i>Hey, one of those machines you asked for</i>
<i>is going crazy.</i>

07:53.931 --> 07:56.517
<i>-[Five] Which one?</i>
<i>-It's the, uh, atmospheric radar.</i>

07:57.435 --> 07:59.812
<i>-[Five] Good.</i>
<i>-I don't get it. What are you tracking?</i>

07:59.896 --> 08:01.063
<i>A hurricane? A storm front?</i>

08:01.147 --> 08:03.399
<i>-Sound waves.</i>
<i>-Sound waves.</i>

08:03.900 --> 08:04.817
<i>[soft beeping]</i>

08:04.901 --> 08:06.527
<i>Wow. What--</i>

08:08.237 --> 08:09.280
<i>Where are you going?</i>

08:12.325 --> 08:13.826
<i>[train horn blows in distance]</i>

08:34.597 --> 08:37.099
<i>-[puffing]</i>
<i>-[children chattering]</i>

08:38.017 --> 08:39.310
<i>[boy 1] Yeah!</i>

08:39.685 --> 08:41.354
<i>[boy 2] Yeah! King Kong!</i>

08:47.109 --> 08:48.277
<i>[Luther] Allison?</i>

08:48.361 --> 08:49.278
<i>[groans]</i>

09:00.456 --> 09:01.457
<i>[chuckles]</i>

09:02.667 --> 09:04.335
<i>-My bad.</i>
<i>-Dipshit.</i>

09:06.212 --> 09:07.129
<i>All right.</i>

09:07.838 --> 09:08.714
<i>Carry on.</i>

09:14.178 --> 09:15.555
<i>[cornstalk snaps]</i>

09:15.638 --> 09:17.598
<i>[approaching footsteps]</i>

09:26.816 --> 09:27.692
<i>[scoffs softly]</i>

09:32.738 --> 09:33.656
<i>Hi, Vanya.</i>

09:34.073 --> 09:35.199
<i>Who are you?</i>

09:35.449 --> 09:36.450
<i>I'm your brother.</i>

09:36.826 --> 09:37.827
<i>I have a brother?</i>

09:38.494 --> 09:41.122
<i>Look, you can either stay here</i>
<i>and wait for the IKEA mafia</i>

09:41.205 --> 09:43.374
<i>to come back to kill you,</i>
<i>or you can come with me.</i>

09:45.626 --> 09:47.128
<i>Wh... Why are they trying to kill me?</i>

09:47.211 --> 09:49.547
<i>'Cause you're not supposed to be here,</i>
<i>Vanya.</i>

09:49.839 --> 09:50.965
<i>In Dallas?</i>

09:51.674 --> 09:53.676
<i>No. Here, in 1963.</i>

10:01.559 --> 10:03.019
<i>Holy shit.</i>

10:03.978 --> 10:05.271
<i>Yeah, pretty wild, right?</i>

10:07.064 --> 10:10.026
<i>It's good to see your powers</i>
<i>are still intact. Let's go.</i>

10:33.215 --> 10:35.801
<i>Goddamn sequins drive me nuts.</i>

10:36.552 --> 10:37.803
<i>-[flips pedal]</i>
<i>-Come on.</i>

10:37.887 --> 10:40.598
<i>[sewing machine whirring]</i>

10:41.390 --> 10:42.767
<i>There he is.</i>

10:42.850 --> 10:44.644
<i>-[dog whines]</i>
<i>-Want me to scramble you an egg? </i>

10:44.727 --> 10:46.896
<i>You need protein after a run like that.</i>

10:46.979 --> 10:48.814
<i>Uh, no, I'm... I'm fine.</i>

10:50.733 --> 10:52.193
<i>[Jack]</i>
<i>Well, you need to eat something.</i>

10:52.276 --> 10:54.153
<i>I need your head in the game</i>
<i>for the fight tonight.</i>

10:54.528 --> 10:57.323
<i>I got a lot of heavy hitters</i>
<i>putting up a lot of dough.</i>

10:57.948 --> 10:59.617
<i>[dog whining]</i>

10:59.700 --> 11:00.534
<i>Hey.</i>

11:01.160 --> 11:02.328
<i>You're up for it, right?</i>

11:02.411 --> 11:04.538
<i>What? Yeah, of course. Yeah.</i>

11:04.914 --> 11:06.707
<i>You know, just... [sighs]</i>

11:06.791 --> 11:08.542
<i>You know people, right?</i>

11:09.168 --> 11:10.461
<i>You know, guys in the department?</i>

11:10.544 --> 11:13.089
<i>Guys that are good at tracking people down</i>
<i>and whatnot?</i>

11:13.631 --> 11:14.965
<i>[dog whines]</i>

11:15.716 --> 11:17.134
<i>Who needs tracking down?</i>

11:17.218 --> 11:19.720
<i>It's just somebody</i>
<i>I thought I'd never see again.</i>

11:20.930 --> 11:22.682
<i>Turns out maybe she's not gone,</i>

11:22.765 --> 11:24.600
<i>maybe I just haven't found her yet.</i>

11:24.684 --> 11:27.311
<i>Well, give me a name,</i>
<i>I'll see what I can do.</i>

11:27.395 --> 11:28.646
<i>Yeah? You sure?</i>

11:28.729 --> 11:32.108
<i>Can't have my number-one guy moping around</i>
<i>like some sad puppy.</i>

11:32.191 --> 11:33.025
<i>[dog whines]</i>

11:33.109 --> 11:34.610
<i>Come on, give me a name.</i>

11:41.033 --> 11:42.159
<i>[Luther] Thank you, Jack.</i>

11:44.537 --> 11:45.663
<i>[Jack] "Hargreeves."</i>

11:46.455 --> 11:48.416
<i>What is she, your ex?</i>

11:49.500 --> 11:50.710
<i>S... Sorta.</i>

11:52.128 --> 11:53.629
<i>Y-Yeah. Sure.</i>

12:09.103 --> 12:10.229
<i>[rings bell]</i>

12:25.244 --> 12:26.328
<i>Klaus?</i>

12:28.998 --> 12:30.666
<i>-Allison.</i>
<i>-Oh! [laughs]</i>

12:30.750 --> 12:31.709
<i>Allison!</i>

12:34.837 --> 12:37.006
<i>-Oh, my God.</i>
<i>-[Allison gasping]</i>

12:37.089 --> 12:38.507
<i>[laughs] Oh, it's really you.</i>

12:38.591 --> 12:41.886
<i>-Oh, my God. Oh, it's been so long.</i>
<i>-[Klaus] I thought you were dead.</i>

12:41.969 --> 12:44.263
<i>-I thought I was the only one left.</i>
<i>-I know. Me too.</i>

12:45.806 --> 12:49.101
<i>Oh, God, sit down, sit down.</i>
<i>We have so much catching up to do.</i>

12:49.185 --> 12:54.190
<i>Yeah. I mean, you want to catch me up</i>
<i>on how you ended up in a place like this?</i>

12:55.357 --> 13:00.654
<i>Oh... you know, dicks, drugs, debutantes.</i>
<i>My holy trinity.</i>

13:00.738 --> 13:01.697
<i>[laughs]</i>

13:01.781 --> 13:03.574
<i>But, yeah, it's been a wild run.</i>

13:03.657 --> 13:04.950
<i>Klaus, you started a cult.</i>

13:05.034 --> 13:08.037
<i>"Cult" is a very negative word, Allison. </i>
<i>We prefer to call it</i>

13:08.120 --> 13:11.040
<i>-"an alternative spiritual community."</i>
<i>-[Allison] Mmm...</i>

13:11.123 --> 13:12.124
<i>Nope.</i>

13:12.374 --> 13:14.376
<i>You definitely started a cult.</i>

13:15.503 --> 13:18.005
<i>All right, all right, all right.</i>
<i>Enough about me. What about you?</i>

13:18.088 --> 13:21.467
<i>-What have you been up to?</i>
<i>-Uh, well, I'm living in South Dallas,</i>

13:21.550 --> 13:23.719
<i>working as a civil rights organizer.</i>

13:23.803 --> 13:24.678
<i>Wow.</i>

13:26.263 --> 13:28.682
<i>-With my husband.</i>
<i>-[gasping]</i>

13:29.308 --> 13:31.644
<i>-[whispers] You're married?</i>
<i>-[chuckles] Yeah.</i>

13:31.727 --> 13:33.020
<i>Who is this lunatic?</i>

13:33.103 --> 13:34.271
<i>[laughs]</i>

13:34.730 --> 13:37.233
<i>His name is Raymond Chestnut.</i>

13:37.691 --> 13:38.526
<i>Ray.</i>

13:39.944 --> 13:41.403
<i>Wait, is he locked up right now?</i>

13:42.279 --> 13:44.281
<i>-Yeah. How do you know that?</i>
<i>-Yeah, yeah.</i>

13:44.365 --> 13:45.449
<i>We did time together.</i>

13:45.533 --> 13:46.367
<i>[chuckles] Wow.</i>

13:46.700 --> 13:47.701
<i>Small world.</i>

13:47.785 --> 13:50.371
<i>We organized a really big sit-in</i>
<i>at a lunch counter today.</i>

13:50.454 --> 13:51.413
<i>[Klaus] Uh-huh.</i>

13:51.497 --> 13:54.875
<i>And then Ray got arrested</i>
<i>on some bullshit charge, and...</i>

13:55.709 --> 13:56.794
<i>I can't get him out.</i>

13:57.002 --> 13:59.338
<i>Hello. Why didn't you just rumor him out?</i>

13:59.672 --> 14:01.465
<i>I haven't used my power since...</i>

14:03.384 --> 14:04.927
<i>I heard a rumor... [echoing]</i>

14:05.010 --> 14:05.970
<i>[Vanya grunts]</i>

14:06.262 --> 14:07.930
<i>[Allison] </i>I couldn't speak for a year.

14:09.265 --> 14:10.182
<i>[Klaus] Ooh.</i>

14:10.266 --> 14:12.685
<i>-Ooh, I'm sorry, Allison.</i>
<i>-[Allison] No, it's okay.</i>

14:12.768 --> 14:15.604
<i>I actually really like who I am</i>
<i>without it.</i>

14:15.688 --> 14:19.024
<i>Everything I have, I've earned,</i>
<i>and it feels </i>really<i> good.</i>

14:19.108 --> 14:20.025
<i>You know?</i>

14:22.611 --> 14:24.613
<i>[pedestrians chatter indistinctly]</i>

14:57.563 --> 14:59.899
<i>-[door bell jingling]</i>
<i>-[tapping loudly]</i>

15:02.109 --> 15:04.486
<i>[Handler] Fish don't like people</i>
<i>tapping on the glass.</i>

15:04.570 --> 15:06.155
<i>-[puppy barks]</i>
<i>-[boy] Why not?</i>

15:06.238 --> 15:07.323
<i>[birds tweeting]</i>

15:07.406 --> 15:09.033
<i>[Handler] It agitates them. </i>

15:10.993 --> 15:12.202
<i>Makes them nervous.</i>

15:14.622 --> 15:17.374
<i>Life is tough enough being so small...</i>

15:18.292 --> 15:21.462
<i>in a world filled with predators...</i>

15:22.171 --> 15:26.759
<i>just waiting for some bigger fish</i>
<i>to come along and gobble you up.</i>

15:26.842 --> 15:29.094
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-What's that on your head?</i>

15:32.890 --> 15:34.350
<i>It's called a bullet wound.</i>

15:35.225 --> 15:36.101
<i>From what?</i>

15:36.769 --> 15:38.312
<i>From getting shot in the head.</i>

15:42.399 --> 15:43.776
<i>Is the bullet still in there?</i>

15:43.859 --> 15:45.027
<i>[laughs softly]</i>

15:45.152 --> 15:46.987
<i>Fragments of it are, yes.</i>

15:47.321 --> 15:48.155
<i>Huh.</i>

15:58.290 --> 16:00.250
<i>[whispers indistinctly]</i>

16:12.846 --> 16:14.264
<i>[door bell jingles]</i>

16:17.142 --> 16:18.519
<i>[door shuts, bell jingling]</i>

16:23.774 --> 16:25.442
<i>-[low chatter]</i>
<i>-[Odessa] All right, Muriel.</i>

16:25.526 --> 16:27.111
<i>-We'll see you next week.</i>
<i>-[door shuts, locks]</i>

16:31.115 --> 16:32.491
<i>How's Ray holding up?</i>

16:34.076 --> 16:35.077
<i>Ray is Ray.</i>

16:35.828 --> 16:37.079
<i>When's he getting out?</i>

16:37.871 --> 16:39.039
<i>I'm working on that.</i>

16:40.040 --> 16:41.542
<i>We need to postpone the sit-in.</i>

16:41.625 --> 16:43.502
<i>[people muttering]</i>

16:43.585 --> 16:44.420
<i>No way.</i>

16:45.504 --> 16:46.422
<i>Excuse me?</i>

16:46.505 --> 16:48.007
<i>Kennedy arrives in five days. </i>

16:48.090 --> 16:50.342
<i>We have to take advantage. We can't wait.</i>

16:50.426 --> 16:51.468
<i>[Odessa] I don't know.</i>

16:51.552 --> 16:53.762
<i>Something doesn't feel right without Ray.</i>

16:53.846 --> 16:55.764
<i>Ray would want us to move forward.</i>

16:55.848 --> 16:57.349
<i>[man] Did he say that to you? </i>

16:57.433 --> 16:58.600
<i>Those exact words?</i>

17:01.020 --> 17:01.979
<i>He didn't have to. </i>

17:02.479 --> 17:04.606
<i>Because this movement</i>
<i>is bigger than all of us.</i>

17:04.690 --> 17:05.691
<i>-Even Ray.</i>
<i>-[man] Mmm.</i>

17:05.774 --> 17:06.817
<i>I'm calling it.</i>

17:08.193 --> 17:09.028
<i>We postpone.</i>

17:09.111 --> 17:10.154
<i>[scoffs]</i>

17:10.529 --> 17:11.822
<i>[man] We postpone.</i>

17:13.866 --> 17:14.825
<i>Why don't we vote on it?</i>

17:14.908 --> 17:16.326
<i>We're not voting on it.</i>

17:16.410 --> 17:19.371
<i>-Why the hell not?</i>
<i>-Because that's not how this works.</i>

17:20.080 --> 17:22.124
<i>You trying to tell me how this works?</i>

17:22.583 --> 17:24.668
<i>In my own damn beauty parlor? What...</i>

17:25.294 --> 17:27.379
<i>you about to start coiffin' hair, too?</i>

17:28.797 --> 17:29.673
<i>No, ma'am.</i>

17:29.757 --> 17:30.841
<i>I didn't think so.</i>

17:34.887 --> 17:37.598
<i>Look, we've been organizing this sit-in</i>
<i>for months. </i>

17:38.640 --> 17:39.892
<i>When Kennedy gets here, </i>

17:40.934 --> 17:42.186
<i>so do the cameras.</i>

17:43.062 --> 17:44.855
<i>Now</i> is the time to show the world

17:44.938 --> 17:47.816
<i>-what it is </i>really like<i> for us down here. </i>
<i>-[murmurs of agreement]</i>

17:47.900 --> 17:52.029
<i>And to show the police that</i>
<i>we will not be </i>bullied<i> into submission. </i>

17:53.280 --> 17:55.032
<i>We will continue to fight for equality,</i>

17:55.115 --> 17:56.867
<i>even in the face of persecution.</i>

17:57.785 --> 17:59.078
<i>With or without Ray. </i>

18:00.662 --> 18:01.705
<i>Because we're ready.</i>

18:04.500 --> 18:05.501
<i>All in favor?</i>

18:15.969 --> 18:17.137
<i>[Odessa] There it is. </i>

18:19.431 --> 18:20.891
<i>"Behind every man..."</i>

18:23.435 --> 18:25.813
<i>[people chattering softly]</i>

18:32.569 --> 18:34.488
<i>-[phone ringing nearby]</i>
<i>-[mutters] Come on.</i>

18:34.571 --> 18:36.240
<i>[typewriter clacking nearby]</i>

18:36.323 --> 18:38.325
<i>[lights buzzing]</i>

18:46.291 --> 18:48.293
<i>[soft squishing]</i>

18:50.879 --> 18:52.214
<i>What in tarnation?</i>

18:59.054 --> 19:01.849
<i>-[exhales sharply]</i>
<i>-[typewriter types slowly]</i>

19:31.336 --> 19:33.881
<i>[typewriter clacking nearby]</i>

19:34.506 --> 19:36.967
<i>-[Klaus] Don't gloat.</i>
<i>-[blows]</i>

19:37.050 --> 19:39.803
<i>-Yeah, yeah, yeah, whatever.</i>
<i>-[Ray] You. You got me out?</i>

19:40.470 --> 19:42.931
<i>[Klaus]</i>
<i>I told you I had friends in </i>high<i> places.</i>

19:44.224 --> 19:45.517
<i>I don't know what to say.</i>

19:45.642 --> 19:46.977
<i>[Klaus] Don't say a word. </i>

19:48.604 --> 19:51.106
<i>Anything</i> for family, brother.

19:51.815 --> 19:53.317
<i>-Well, okay. </i>
<i>-[Klaus chuckles]</i>

19:53.400 --> 19:56.111
<i>-Yeah!</i>
<i>-We are all brothers </i>

19:56.195 --> 19:57.738
<i>-beneath the skin.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

19:57.863 --> 19:59.531
<i>No, literally.</i>

20:00.490 --> 20:01.825
<i>You're my brother-in-law.</i>

20:03.619 --> 20:05.621
<i>-What?</i>
<i>-[chuckles] Yeah, man.</i>

20:05.913 --> 20:09.708
<i>Family barbecues</i>
<i>are about to get real weird.</i>

20:09.791 --> 20:10.834
<i>[laughs softly]</i>

20:11.293 --> 20:12.169
<i>Later.</i>

20:20.802 --> 20:21.887
<i>Leave the pot, dear.</i>

20:22.429 --> 20:23.305
<i>Thank you.</i>

20:24.097 --> 20:25.390
<i>Lippy little shit.</i>

20:26.725 --> 20:28.852
<i>You gonna tell me</i>
<i>what the hell's going on?</i>

20:29.519 --> 20:32.814
<i>When you were a baby, you were bought</i>
<i>by an eccentric billionaire.</i>

20:33.482 --> 20:35.817
<i>He raised you in an elite academy </i>

20:35.901 --> 20:38.320
<i>with six other siblings</i>
<i>with extraordinary powers,</i>

20:38.403 --> 20:41.823
<i>but in the year 2019,</i>
<i>in order to avoid the apocalypse,</i>

20:41.907 --> 20:43.200
<i>we jumped into a vortex </i>

20:43.283 --> 20:47.287
<i>and ended up being scattered</i>
<i>throughout the timeline in Dallas, Texas.</i>

20:50.123 --> 20:51.124
<i>Any questions?</i>

20:52.626 --> 20:54.378
<i>What do you mean, "the apocalypse"?</i>

20:56.255 --> 20:58.423
<i>I mean the end of the world as we know it.</i>

20:58.632 --> 20:59.633
<i>Yeah, but how?</i>

21:00.342 --> 21:01.718
<i>You really don't remember anything?</i>

21:01.802 --> 21:03.720
<i>No, nothing before a month ago.</i>

21:03.804 --> 21:05.138
<i>Then what do you remember?</i>

21:08.141 --> 21:09.726
<i>I landed in, like, a...</i>

21:10.018 --> 21:11.228
<i>back alley.</i>

21:11.311 --> 21:12.646
<i>Got hit by a car.</i>

21:12.729 --> 21:15.274
<i>My head was ringing like crazy.</i>

21:15.357 --> 21:17.776
<i>I had no idea how I got there,</i>
<i>where I came from.</i>

21:19.278 --> 21:20.821
<i>What causes the apocalypse?</i>

21:26.493 --> 21:27.744
<i>Asteroid impact.</i>

21:28.412 --> 21:30.414
<i>The big kaboom ends everything.</i>

21:31.123 --> 21:34.376
<i>Just like the one that got the dinosaurs,</i>
<i>except way worse.</i>

21:35.252 --> 21:37.212
<i>Bad news is, it followed us here.</i>

21:39.923 --> 21:41.550
<i>What do you mean, "followed us"?</i>

21:42.759 --> 21:45.971
<i>Eight days from now,</i>
<i>the world ends in a nuclear doomsday.</i>

21:46.555 --> 21:49.558
<i>It's a different disease, but...</i>
<i>same result.</i>

21:53.353 --> 21:54.396
<i>That can't be right.</i>

21:54.771 --> 21:55.772
<i>I saw it.</i>

21:56.565 --> 21:57.733
<i>With my own eyes.</i>

21:58.942 --> 22:01.111
<i>[sighs] You were there.</i>

22:03.280 --> 22:04.197
<i>We all were.</i>

22:06.325 --> 22:07.242
<i>Shit.</i>

22:07.659 --> 22:08.869
<i>I need to make a phone call.</i>

22:09.619 --> 22:10.537
<i>Vanya.</i>

22:11.496 --> 22:13.498
<i>[slow classical music plays on LP]</i>

22:17.627 --> 22:21.048
<i>[record skipping]</i>

22:24.092 --> 22:25.886
<i>-[screeching]</i>
<i>-[faster classical music playing]</i>

22:26.011 --> 22:28.430
<i>[Sissy]</i>
<i>Oh, God. Let Mama help you, honey.</i>

22:28.513 --> 22:30.140
<i>Hey, let Mama help you. It's okay.</i>

22:30.640 --> 22:31.641
<i>Here we go.</i>

22:32.768 --> 22:33.894
<i>-Okay.</i>
<i>-[screeches]</i>

22:33.977 --> 22:35.062
<i>-Oh, honey.</i>
<i>-Mmm!</i>

22:35.145 --> 22:37.105
<i>Honey, just take a deep breath.</i>
<i>Deep breath, honey.</i>

22:37.189 --> 22:39.733
<i>-Just breathe. Just breathe.</i>
<i>-Mmm!</i>

22:39.816 --> 22:41.026
<i>-It's okay, babe--</i>
<i>-Mmm!</i>

22:41.109 --> 22:42.110
<i>Harlan.</i>

22:42.194 --> 22:43.862
<i>-Harlan, stop it!</i>
<i>-[Harlan] Mmm!</i>

22:43.945 --> 22:45.155
<i>Harlan! Harlan, stop it, honey.</i>

22:45.238 --> 22:46.490
<i>-Mmm!</i>
<i>-Stop it!</i>

22:46.782 --> 22:48.450
<i>-[Harlan screeches]</i>
<i>-[screams]</i>

22:49.117 --> 22:52.913
<i>-[pants] Baby, come on. Relax. I gotcha.</i>
<i>-[phone ringing]</i>

22:52.996 --> 22:55.832
<i>I gotcha. You're okay. You're okay.</i>
<i>You're okay.</i>

22:55.916 --> 22:57.501
<i>-Oh, shit.</i>
<i>-Mmm!</i>

22:57.584 --> 23:00.003
<i>-Okay, here we go. Here we go.</i>
<i>-[ringing continues]</i>

23:00.087 --> 23:01.088
<i>You're okay.</i>

23:01.922 --> 23:04.049
<i>[panting]</i>

23:04.132 --> 23:05.509
<i>-Shit.</i>
<i>-Mmm.</i>

23:06.676 --> 23:09.388
<i>-[phone continues ringing]</i>
<i>-[Harlan] Mmm!</i>

23:11.723 --> 23:12.974
<i>-Hello?</i>
<i>-[Vanya] </i>Sissy?

23:13.058 --> 23:13.892
<i>Vanya?</i>

23:13.975 --> 23:15.227
<i>Where are you?</i>

23:15.310 --> 23:17.354
<i>I'm so sorry I took the station wagon.</i>

23:17.437 --> 23:20.524
<i>[exhales sharply]</i>
<i>I don't care about the damn car.</i>

23:20.607 --> 23:21.775
<i>[gasps, panting]</i>

23:21.858 --> 23:22.984
<i>Are you okay?</i>

23:23.235 --> 23:25.445
<i>-[Vanya] </i>I'm fine.
<i>-What the hell happened?</i>

23:27.406 --> 23:28.865
<i>I found my younger brother.</i>

23:28.949 --> 23:29.825
<i>[Sissy] </i>What?

23:30.200 --> 23:31.535
<i>H-How?</i>

23:31.618 --> 23:32.828
<i>It's a long story.</i>

23:33.453 --> 23:34.454
<i>Is Harlan okay?</i>

23:35.038 --> 23:35.914
<i>[sighs]</i>

23:36.957 --> 23:38.750
<i>No, he's... he's... he's not okay.</i>

23:38.834 --> 23:41.253
<i>The record player broke, and he just...</i>

23:41.711 --> 23:43.755
<i>Just-- [sighs]</i>
<i>When the hell are you coming back?</i>

23:43.839 --> 23:45.715
<i>As soon as I can, I promise.</i>

23:47.426 --> 23:48.927
<i>I'm happy you found your real family--</i>

23:49.010 --> 23:50.303
<i>-[coin rattles]</i>
<i>-[dial tone]</i>

23:50.387 --> 23:52.139
<i>-What the hell?</i>
<i>-We don't have time for this.</i>

23:52.222 --> 23:53.807
<i>That's my friend you just hung up on.</i>

23:53.890 --> 23:54.808
<i>Listen to me.</i>

23:55.392 --> 23:58.270
<i>[softly] Those people from the field</i>
<i>are coming after us.</i>

23:58.437 --> 23:59.896
<i>They are never going to stop.</i>

24:01.606 --> 24:02.732
<i>Do you understand me?</i>

24:03.483 --> 24:05.068
<i>We need to stick together,</i>

24:05.277 --> 24:07.863
<i>find the others,</i>
<i>figure out how to stop doomsday.</i>

24:08.530 --> 24:09.948
<i>Whoever this person is,</i>

24:10.031 --> 24:12.951
<i>they can't be more important</i>
<i>than the end of the world.</i>

24:14.995 --> 24:16.037
<i>We need to go.</i>

24:24.713 --> 24:26.298
<i>[faint beeping nearby]</i>

24:26.381 --> 24:27.507
<i>[grunts softly]</i>

24:28.425 --> 24:29.634
<i>[exhales]</i>

24:30.343 --> 24:31.178
<i>You hungry?</i>

24:31.261 --> 24:33.346
<i>-Elliott's made moldy tuna.</i>
<i>-[Elliott splutters]</i>

24:33.430 --> 24:35.765
<i>It's a tuna </i>mold.

24:36.016 --> 24:36.850
<i>[Diego] I'll pass.</i>

24:36.933 --> 24:38.935
<i>-Where's my shirt?</i>
<i>-Where do you think you're going?</i>

24:39.019 --> 24:42.397
<i>This is all connected to JFK,</i>
<i>and my dad's right in the middle of it.</i>

24:43.064 --> 24:45.567
<i>That's why he attacked me last night.</i>

24:45.650 --> 24:46.985
<i>[grunting exhale]</i>

24:47.068 --> 24:49.654
<i>'Cause he knows that I'm actually</i>
<i>getting closer to-- [yells]</i>

24:50.780 --> 24:51.740
<i>[grunts]</i>

24:52.032 --> 24:55.660
<i>Yeah, you're in </i>such<i> a fit state to fight.</i>
<i>You should probably go right now.</i>

24:55.744 --> 24:57.037
<i>What is wrong with you?</i>

24:57.120 --> 24:59.122
<i>You almost got killed last night.</i>

24:59.664 --> 25:01.333
<i>-Take a day off.</i>
<i>-[Diego grunts]</i>

25:07.255 --> 25:09.591
<i>I can't believe I got shanked</i>
<i>by my own father.</i>

25:09.966 --> 25:10.884
<i>I know.</i>

25:10.967 --> 25:12.427
<i>So rude.</i>

25:13.553 --> 25:15.055
<i>Hey, if it's any consolation,</i>

25:15.138 --> 25:18.099
<i>he probably didn't know</i>
<i>that you were his son when he shanked you.</i>

25:18.183 --> 25:19.059
<i>[Diego] Still...</i>

25:21.394 --> 25:22.854
<i>he cheap-shotted me.</i>

25:22.938 --> 25:24.898
<i>[soft piano melody playing]</i>

25:24.981 --> 25:28.068
<i>Man to man, that son of a bitch</i>
<i>wouldn't stand a chance.</i>

25:29.569 --> 25:31.613
<i>-Of course he wouldn't. [taps skin]</i>
<i>-[gasps softly]</i>

25:34.574 --> 25:35.951
<i>Why were you following me?</i>

25:38.662 --> 25:42.207
<i>[sighs]</i>
<i>I thought you were taking off on me.</i>

25:42.916 --> 25:43.959
<i>Mmm.</i>

25:44.709 --> 25:45.794
<i>What people do.</i>

25:50.549 --> 25:51.508
<i>Hey, um...</i>

25:54.678 --> 25:56.388
<i>you know, when you were lying there,</i>

25:58.056 --> 25:59.599
<i>I... I thought you were dead.</i>

26:01.017 --> 26:02.644
<i>That's how I found my parents.</i>

26:06.731 --> 26:08.733
<i>Facedown in the living room.</i>

26:11.444 --> 26:12.904
<i>It was a home invasion.</i>

26:16.074 --> 26:16.950
<i>[whispers] Shit.</i>

26:19.494 --> 26:20.704
<i>How old were you?</i>

26:22.372 --> 26:23.290
<i>Four.</i>

26:26.668 --> 26:28.461
<i>You never talked about that in group.</i>

26:31.631 --> 26:33.883
<i>I never talked about that with anyone.</i>

26:38.722 --> 26:41.266
<i>If you wanna stay longer...</i>

26:43.268 --> 26:44.185
<i>for a bit...</i>

26:45.604 --> 26:46.813
<i>I guess that's okay.</i>

26:48.315 --> 26:49.190
<i>Yeah?</i>

26:50.442 --> 26:51.359
<i>Yeah.</i>

26:54.154 --> 26:57.032
<i>Is it okay that I don't hate you</i>
<i>like I hate most people?</i>

26:58.533 --> 27:00.076
<i>[laughs softly]</i>

27:02.287 --> 27:03.163
<i>Yeah.</i>

27:03.913 --> 27:05.290
<i>Yeah, that's okay by me.</i>

27:09.252 --> 27:11.338
<i>-Jesus!</i>
<i>-What the hell do you think you're doing?</i>

27:11.421 --> 27:13.423
<i>I don't understand you!</i>

27:14.883 --> 27:16.051
<i>[sighs heavily]</i>

27:20.055 --> 27:22.557
<i>-Ow. Oh, oh, ow, ow, ow, ow...</i>
<i>-Too much?</i>

27:22.974 --> 27:23.808
<i>Just...</i>

27:24.934 --> 27:26.061
<i>be gentle.</i>

27:26.144 --> 27:27.103
<i>Never.</i>

27:37.697 --> 27:38.948
<i>[Elliott] Mmm...</i>

27:39.407 --> 27:40.617
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

27:41.493 --> 27:42.494
<i>[loud thud]</i>

27:47.957 --> 27:48.917
<i>[loud clatter]</i>

27:52.712 --> 27:54.714
<i>[sinister instrumental music playing]</i>

28:23.201 --> 28:25.120
<i>Don't ever say</i>
<i>I never did nothing for you,</i>

28:25.203 --> 28:27.122
<i>-you big galoot.</i>
<i>-[dog whines]</i>

28:28.289 --> 28:29.457
<i>[muffled] You found her?</i>

28:29.541 --> 28:30.792
<i>South Dallas.</i>

28:30.875 --> 28:32.669
<i>It's a hell of a place. [chuckles]</i>

28:33.002 --> 28:35.755
<i>You sure know how to pick 'em. [cackling]</i>

28:36.172 --> 28:38.299
<i>[Joe Tex's</i>
<i>"I'll Never Do You Wrong" plays]</i>

28:38.383 --> 28:43.263
<i>♪ If I ever do you wrong ♪</i>

28:44.681 --> 28:49.769
<i>♪ If I ever leave you all alone ♪</i>

28:50.854 --> 28:56.526
<i>♪ If I ever tell you a lie ♪</i>

28:56.735 --> 29:01.656
<i>♪ And if I ever make you cry ♪</i>

29:02.073 --> 29:04.367
<i>♪ Baby, I hope a fly ♪</i>

29:04.451 --> 29:05.910
<i>♪ I hope a fly ♪</i>

29:05.994 --> 29:08.997
<i>-♪ Light on my pie ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Light on my pie ♪</i>

29:09.080 --> 29:13.585
<i>♪ I hope a bee sting me</i>
<i>Over my eye ♪</i>

29:13.668 --> 29:15.253
<i>♪ Over my eye... ♪</i>

29:15.587 --> 29:16.796
<i>[Ray] Can I help you?</i>

29:18.298 --> 29:19.257
<i>[Luther] Oh.</i>

29:19.883 --> 29:22.135
<i>I'm sorry,</i>
<i>I must have the wrong address. I...</i>

29:22.635 --> 29:23.762
<i>Who you looking for?</i>

29:24.471 --> 29:25.597
<i>Allison Hargreeves.</i>

29:25.930 --> 29:27.265
<i>You mean Allison Chestnut.</i>

29:28.975 --> 29:29.851
<i>Chestnut?</i>

29:31.144 --> 29:32.020
<i>[Ray] My wife.</i>

29:38.151 --> 29:39.402
<i>[inhales deeply]</i>

29:43.531 --> 29:45.074
<i>Would you mind if I, uh...</i>

29:45.784 --> 29:46.785
<i>Knock yourself out.</i>

29:47.368 --> 29:48.453
<i>[lid opens]</i>

30:01.841 --> 30:03.384
<i>[muffled] I'm sorry, did you want one?</i>

30:03.468 --> 30:04.594
<i>[Ray] No, thank you.</i>

30:05.678 --> 30:08.348
<i>Allison told me</i>
<i>that she had family up north, but...</i>

30:08.848 --> 30:10.391
<i>she never mentioned a brother.</i>

30:10.767 --> 30:13.061
<i>And she certainly</i>
<i>never mentioned a brother</i>

30:13.144 --> 30:14.354
<i>that looked like you.</i>

30:17.816 --> 30:20.151
<i>I guess we haven't been that close lately.</i>

30:20.443 --> 30:21.319
<i>[Ray] Mmm.</i>

30:23.488 --> 30:25.031
<i>So you staying here in Dallas?</i>

30:25.240 --> 30:26.199
<i>[Luther] I got a room</i>

30:26.282 --> 30:29.494
<i>at the Plano Street Rooming House</i>
<i>for Solitary Men.</i>

30:29.577 --> 30:30.495
<i>[Ray] Oh, yeah?</i>

30:30.578 --> 30:31.704
<i>How you like it?</i>

30:31.788 --> 30:32.747
<i>Not bad.</i>

30:33.414 --> 30:34.374
<i>Clean.</i>

30:35.416 --> 30:36.793
<i>Reasonable rates.</i>

30:36.876 --> 30:37.752
<i>Good.</i>

30:39.629 --> 30:41.548
<i>-Very good.</i>
<i>-[Luther] So, uh...</i>

30:44.509 --> 30:45.760
<i>how long you been married?</i>

30:46.594 --> 30:48.596
<i>Oh, yeah, we're coming up on a year now.</i>

30:55.854 --> 30:57.772
<i>That's so great.</i>

31:03.027 --> 31:03.945
<i>Yeah.</i>

31:04.946 --> 31:06.072
<i>Congratulations.</i>

31:07.240 --> 31:08.157
<i>Thank you.</i>

31:09.242 --> 31:11.202
<i>[phone rings]</i>

31:12.036 --> 31:12.954
<i>[Ray] Hello?</i>

31:14.831 --> 31:16.332
<i>What? We're still on?</i>

31:17.083 --> 31:18.126
<i>I'll be right there.</i>

31:19.252 --> 31:20.336
<i>[hangs up phone]</i>

31:20.712 --> 31:22.672
<i>[Ray] Listen, I have got to run.</i>

31:22.755 --> 31:25.341
<i>Do you want to leave a message</i>
<i>for Allison?</i>

31:31.764 --> 31:34.267
<i>[Luther] Would you just tell her</i>
<i>that I need to talk to her?</i>

31:35.894 --> 31:36.895
<i>Sure.</i>

31:40.064 --> 31:42.066
<i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

31:46.529 --> 31:47.780
<i>[chatter ceases]</i>

31:47.864 --> 31:49.782
<i>[woman] What? [gasps]</i>

32:02.629 --> 32:03.463
<i>Out.</i>

32:03.880 --> 32:05.423
<i>Else I'm calling the police.</i>

32:05.506 --> 32:07.091
<i>I'd like to be served, please.</i>

32:08.635 --> 32:10.053
<i>Can't you read, girl?</i>

32:10.929 --> 32:12.180
<i>Seven languages.</i>

32:12.597 --> 32:15.266
<i>Oh. You a smart one, huh?</i>

32:15.850 --> 32:16.893
<i>[door opens]</i>

32:34.327 --> 32:36.120
<i>We'd like to be served, please.</i>

32:42.794 --> 32:45.630
<i>You are not welcome here.</i>

32:52.470 --> 32:54.013
<i>[Ben] The hell are we doing here?</i>

32:54.097 --> 32:56.140
<i>S-Some ole DIY?</i>

32:56.224 --> 32:58.559
<i>You just stay here, pumpkin.</i>

33:00.186 --> 33:01.104
<i>Okay.</i>

33:10.613 --> 33:12.073
<i>[Ben] Don't do anything dumb.</i>

33:36.639 --> 33:37.515
<i>David?</i>

33:37.724 --> 33:39.225
<i>[man] Uh, yeah, can I help you?</i>

33:42.061 --> 33:42.979
<i>Dave?</i>

33:43.730 --> 33:46.357
<i>Yeah, that's what it says</i>
<i>on my name tag, yeah.</i>

33:49.152 --> 33:50.236
<i>[exhales sharply]</i>

33:51.487 --> 33:53.865
<i>[voice trembles] Look at you, with your...</i>

33:53.948 --> 33:55.324
<i>jokes and...</i>

33:56.159 --> 33:57.660
<i>your name tag and...</i>

33:58.369 --> 34:00.204
<i>Well, can I help you find anything?</i>

34:00.663 --> 34:01.539
<i>Uh...</i>

34:02.707 --> 34:04.292
<i>[Ben] So </i>this<i> is why we came to Dallas.</i>

34:05.668 --> 34:06.669
<i>[Klaus sighs] I--</i>

34:06.753 --> 34:08.504
<i>You know, this might be</i>
<i>your dumbest idea yet,</i>

34:08.588 --> 34:10.631
<i>-and you're pretty dumb.</i>
<i>-Just, don't.</i>

34:11.049 --> 34:12.842
<i>-You all right, mister?</i>
<i>-Yeah. No, I'm--</i>

34:12.925 --> 34:15.845
<i>-No, he's not all right.</i>
<i>-I'm totally fine. I'm totally fine.</i>

34:15.928 --> 34:17.430
<i>-I just, um--</i>
<i>-You just what?</i>

34:18.473 --> 34:21.225
<i>[sighs, breath trembling]</i>

34:22.477 --> 34:23.811
<i>-Paint.</i>
<i>-Paint?</i>

34:23.895 --> 34:25.521
<i>-Paint?</i>
<i>-Yeah, I'm...</i>

34:25.897 --> 34:27.940
<i>remodeling the second bathroom and...</i>

34:28.274 --> 34:29.442
<i>require some paint.</i>

34:30.109 --> 34:32.653
<i>Yeah, s-sure thing. What...</i>
<i>What color paint were you looking for?</i>

34:33.196 --> 34:34.447
<i>Oh... [sighs]</i>

34:34.655 --> 34:36.157
<i>...I don't know. [chuckles softly]</i>

34:36.449 --> 34:37.366
<i>Eggshell?</i>

34:37.450 --> 34:39.994
<i>"Egg... Eggshell."</i>
<i>How do you mean, "eggshell"?</i>

34:41.329 --> 34:42.330
<i>As in...</i>

34:43.414 --> 34:44.832
<i>you know, like, white.</i>

34:44.916 --> 34:46.918
<i>Or... Or, like, off-white,</i>

34:47.001 --> 34:49.504
<i>-like an eggshell?</i>
<i>-We're fresh out of white,</i>

34:49.587 --> 34:50.922
<i>but I do have...</i>

34:51.547 --> 34:55.218
<i>Mamie pink on special, which always</i>
<i>goes very nice in the latrine.</i>

34:56.094 --> 34:57.136
<i>That sounds perfect.</i>

34:57.887 --> 34:59.388
<i>Is this considered stalking?</i>

34:59.472 --> 35:01.474
<i>'Cause I think you're stalking now.</i>

35:01.557 --> 35:02.600
<i>[hissing whisper] Shut up!</i>

35:05.561 --> 35:06.938
<i>[levers squeaking]</i>

35:09.148 --> 35:11.234
<i>You're pretty good at that. [chuckles]</i>

35:11.359 --> 35:12.485
<i>Thanks. [laughs softly]</i>

35:12.944 --> 35:14.946
<i>[loud rattling]</i>

35:17.782 --> 35:20.827
<i>-[rattling continues]</i>
<i>-[helicopter blades thumping, distant]</i>

35:25.248 --> 35:27.208
<i>-[overlapping gunfire]</i>
<i>-[Klaus] Dave!</i>

35:28.167 --> 35:29.544
<i>Dave! Dave!</i>

35:29.627 --> 35:31.170
<i>[sobbing] Stay with me, Dave.</i>

35:33.965 --> 35:35.424
<i>[whimpers, echoing] Dave...</i>

35:38.219 --> 35:39.137
<i>[Dave] All set.</i>

35:40.721 --> 35:42.306
<i>-Thanks.</i>
<i>-[Dave] You're welcome.</i>

35:46.227 --> 35:47.854
<i>[exhaling] Yeah.</i>

36:04.120 --> 36:06.789
<i>So this is why you dragged me away</i>
<i>from San Francisco,</i>

36:06.873 --> 36:08.916
<i>so you could rekindle</i>
<i>your little Vietnam fling?</i>

36:09.000 --> 36:11.335
<i>Why don't you stay out of my business,</i>
<i>Casper?</i>

36:11.419 --> 36:14.881
<i>-Your business</i> is<i> my business.</i>
<i>-Oh, well, then, congratulations,</i>

36:15.381 --> 36:17.049
<i>because you're fired!</i>

36:17.758 --> 36:18.593
<i>[starts engine]</i>

36:18.676 --> 36:21.137
<i>-This is wrong, Klaus. It's selfish. </i>
<i>-[Klaus] Just stop, Ben.</i>

36:21.220 --> 36:24.223
<i>-You're just gonna confuse the kid!</i>
<i>-Would you stop? Damn it, listen to me.</i>

36:25.183 --> 36:29.103
<i>When we were on leave in Saigon,</i>
<i>Dave told me about the day he enlisted.</i>

36:29.187 --> 36:30.980
<i>It was the same day</i>
<i>that Kennedy was murdered.</i>

36:31.063 --> 36:35.776
<i>And if you would just please</i>
<i>leave me alone for five goddamn minutes, </i>

36:35.860 --> 36:38.905
<i>then maybe I could convince him</i>
<i>not to sign up to that stupid war</i>

36:38.988 --> 36:40.740
<i>and maybe I could save his life!</i>

36:42.200 --> 36:43.993
<i>[sighs] God damn it!</i>

36:45.786 --> 36:46.787
<i>Ow.</i>

36:47.788 --> 36:49.081
<i>[hisses softly]</i>

36:50.082 --> 36:50.917
<i>Look...</i>

36:51.417 --> 36:53.711
<i>just promise me you can handle this. </i>

36:54.212 --> 36:55.463
<i>Whatever happens.</i>

36:55.546 --> 36:58.424
<i>Yeah, yeah, I can handle it,</i>
<i>I can handle it.</i>

36:58.507 --> 37:01.052
<i>[police sirens wailing]</i>

37:04.805 --> 37:06.349
<i>Oh, shit. Allison.</i>

37:06.807 --> 37:08.809
<i>[overlapping shouts]</i>

37:12.521 --> 37:14.982
<i>[woman 1] You don't belong here!</i>

37:15.691 --> 37:17.318
<i>Get outta here!</i>

37:24.867 --> 37:27.662
<i>-[woman 2] Get them out of here!</i>
<i>-[man 1] Get the hell out of here!</i>

37:27.745 --> 37:29.497
<i>-What the hell?</i>
<i>-What you doing in here, boy?</i>

37:29.580 --> 37:32.625
<i>-What the hell? Come on, go! Get out!</i>
<i>-Get the hell out!</i>

37:33.626 --> 37:35.544
<i>Ray. Oh, you made it. Thank God.</i>

37:35.628 --> 37:36.754
<i>I'm sorry I'm late.</i>

37:36.837 --> 37:38.589
<i>It's been a very interesting day.</i>

37:38.923 --> 37:40.675
<i>[man 2] You can get out!</i>

37:40.758 --> 37:43.344
<i>Take my seat.</i>
<i>Next shift's about to start anyway.</i>

37:43.427 --> 37:46.555
<i>-[overlapping shouts continue]</i>
<i>-Get the hell outta here!</i>

37:48.307 --> 37:49.600
<i>Get out!</i>

37:50.309 --> 37:52.103
<i>Stay the hell outta here!</i>

37:52.478 --> 37:56.565
<i>Do you hear us? We don't want you here.</i>
<i>Come on!</i>

37:58.401 --> 37:59.902
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[crowd groans]</i>

38:00.736 --> 38:03.072
<i>[both grunting]</i>

38:05.157 --> 38:06.284
<i>[Luther groans]</i>

38:09.078 --> 38:10.204
<i>[growls]</i>

38:11.289 --> 38:13.499
<i>-[groans]</i>
<i>-[Luther grunts]</i>

38:13.582 --> 38:15.376
<i>Come on! Come on!</i>

38:15.459 --> 38:16.502
<i>[roars]</i>

38:16.585 --> 38:18.587
<i>[crowd cheers, shouts]</i>

38:19.046 --> 38:20.172
<i>[man] Come on! Get up!</i>

38:22.591 --> 38:25.052
<i>[crowd applauding, shouting]</i>

38:30.016 --> 38:31.058
<i>[grunts]</i>

38:31.183 --> 38:33.477
<i>[crowd roars]</i>

38:39.775 --> 38:41.402
<i>[sounds fading]</i>

38:41.485 --> 38:44.071
<i>-[Ray, echoing] </i>Who you looking for?
<i>-[Luther] </i>Allison Hargreeves.

38:44.155 --> 38:45.740
<i>[Ray] </i>You mean Allison Chestnut.

38:46.407 --> 38:47.283
<i>My wife.</i>

38:48.909 --> 38:50.411
<i>[crowd continues shouting]</i>

38:50.494 --> 38:51.370
<i>[heavy grunt]</i>

38:53.497 --> 38:55.207
<i>-Let's go!</i>
<i>-Come on!</i>

38:56.375 --> 38:58.586
<i>-[Luther grunts]</i>
<i>-[crowd shouting]</i>

39:01.088 --> 39:02.048
<i>What?</i>

39:02.381 --> 39:03.716
<i>Look, he's pummeling him.</i>

39:04.550 --> 39:06.218
<i>-Hit me again.</i>
<i>-The hell are you doing?</i>

39:07.845 --> 39:08.846
<i>[opponent growls]</i>

39:08.929 --> 39:11.599
<i>-Oh, my God, Luther.</i>
<i>-Why isn't he fighting back?</i>

39:13.225 --> 39:14.393
<i>[Luther groans]</i>

39:16.354 --> 39:17.188
<i>[grunts]</i>

39:17.271 --> 39:18.773
<i>[protesters] No more back door!</i>

39:18.856 --> 39:20.274
<i>No more back door!</i>

39:20.358 --> 39:22.026
<i>No more back door!</i>

39:22.109 --> 39:23.486
<i>No more back door!</i>

39:23.569 --> 39:25.071
<i>No more back door!</i>

39:25.154 --> 39:26.655
<i>No more back door!</i>

39:26.739 --> 39:30.951
<i>Get out! Get out! Get out!</i>
<i>Get out! Get out!</i>

39:31.035 --> 39:32.578
<i>-What's wrong?</i>
<i>-[chanting continues]</i>

39:32.661 --> 39:34.330
<i>I got bailed out of jail today</i>

39:34.747 --> 39:39.168
<i>by a very unique character</i>
<i>claiming to be my brother-in-law.</i>

39:39.418 --> 39:40.920
<i>Okay, that... that's Klaus.</i>

39:41.003 --> 39:43.589
<i>-I... I can explain all of that--</i>
<i>-And then I come home</i>

39:44.131 --> 39:46.509
<i>to find the biggest white boy</i>
<i>I've ever seen in my entire life</i>

39:46.592 --> 39:50.429
<i>standing on my front porch,</i>
<i>trembling like somebody's lost puppy,</i>

39:51.097 --> 39:54.433
<i>and the strange thing is,</i>
<i>he is also claiming to be your brother.</i>

39:55.101 --> 39:55.935
<i>Luther.</i>

39:57.686 --> 39:59.397
<i>-That's the one.</i>
<i>-[gasps, shrieks]</i>

39:59.855 --> 40:00.773
<i>[gasps]</i>

40:01.232 --> 40:03.651
<i>-Get your hands off her!</i>
<i>-That's it! You're outta here!</i>

40:03.734 --> 40:05.194
<i>-[whistle trills]</i>
<i>-[grunts, panting]</i>

40:05.277 --> 40:06.862
<i>-Ray!</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

40:07.279 --> 40:09.031
<i>-No, no, no, Ray!</i>
<i>-Allison!</i>

40:09.115 --> 40:11.158
<i>-No, no!</i>
<i>-[whistle trilling]</i>

40:11.867 --> 40:14.036
<i>-No!</i>
<i>-Let her go! Stop it!</i>

40:14.120 --> 40:16.247
<i>[officer]</i>
<i>Get your hands up! Everybody, hands up!</i>

40:16.580 --> 40:19.291
<i>-[blows landing]</i>
<i>-[shouts continue]</i>

40:19.959 --> 40:21.502
<i>[Ray groaning]</i>

40:21.585 --> 40:22.753
<i>Ray!</i>

40:23.295 --> 40:26.549
<i>-[Odessa] Take your hands off her!</i>
<i>-No, stop it! Stop it! Stop it!</i>

40:26.632 --> 40:28.217
<i>-Allison!</i>
<i>-[protesters shouting]</i>

40:28.300 --> 40:29.718
<i>-Let her go!</i>
<i>-No!</i>

40:29.802 --> 40:31.554
<i>Allison!</i>

40:31.637 --> 40:33.973
<i>We have a right to be here!</i>
<i>You let her go!</i>

40:34.056 --> 40:35.433
<i>[Allison gasping]</i>

40:37.518 --> 40:41.313
<i>No more back door! No more back door!</i>
<i>No more back door!</i>

40:43.315 --> 40:45.609
<i>[officer over bullhorn]</i>
<i>Disperse or you will be arrested.</i>

40:45.693 --> 40:47.069
<i>Get your hands off me!</i>

40:47.153 --> 40:48.362
<i>[screaming]</i>

40:48.696 --> 40:50.656
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[woman screaming]</i>

40:50.739 --> 40:51.574
<i>Ray!</i>

40:51.657 --> 40:52.950
<i>-[Ray grunts]</i>
<i>-[screams continue]</i>

40:53.033 --> 40:55.494
<i>Ray! Ray! No!</i>

40:55.578 --> 40:58.456
<i>-Stop it! Get off of him! Stop!</i>
<i>-[officer] You don't belong in there, boy!</i>

40:59.039 --> 41:00.291
<i>-[Allison] No!</i>
<i>-You're next!</i>

41:00.374 --> 41:02.293
<i>[muted shouts]</i>

41:07.047 --> 41:09.216
<i>-Stop it! You're killing him!</i>
<i>-[man] Get off her!</i>

41:12.136 --> 41:14.597
<i>[echoing]</i>
<i>I heard a rumor... that you walked away.</i>

41:18.642 --> 41:20.102
<i>[baton clattering]</i>

41:21.061 --> 41:23.939
<i>-[crowd shouting chaotically]</i>
<i>-[police sirens wailing]</i>

41:29.653 --> 41:33.073
<i>-Ray. Are you... Are you hurt? We're okay.</i>
<i>-[Ray] What did you say to him?</i>

41:33.157 --> 41:34.783
<i>What the hell did you say to him?</i>

41:35.576 --> 41:37.745
<i>-Uh...</i>
<i>-What the hell did you say to him?</i>

41:37.828 --> 41:40.456
<i>-I just told him to leave you alone.</i>
<i>-[Ray] There ain't no way in hell</i>

41:40.539 --> 41:43.542
<i>that a white cop is just gonna walk away</i>
<i>'cause a black woman tells him to.</i>

41:43.626 --> 41:46.003
<i>[coughs] Ray, we don't...</i>
<i>we don't have time for this. Come on.</i>

41:46.086 --> 41:47.463
<i>We gotta go! Gotta get out of here.</i>

41:47.546 --> 41:48.589
<i>-Come on!</i>
<i>-Who are you?</i>

41:48.672 --> 41:49.924
<i>Ray! Ray!</i>

41:50.007 --> 41:52.092
<i>-[coughs] Ray, we-- Ray! Ray--</i>
<i>-[Ray] Who are you?</i>

41:52.176 --> 41:53.469
<i>[coughing]</i>

41:53.552 --> 41:54.678
<i>-[Klaus] Allison.</i>
<i>-Ray!</i>

41:54.762 --> 41:56.764
<i>-Allison, come on. We have to go.</i>
<i>-No, no!</i>

41:56.847 --> 41:59.266
<i>-I can't leave him! Ray!</i>
<i>-[Klaus] Come on! Right now!</i>

41:59.350 --> 42:00.267
<i>Ray!</i>

42:00.351 --> 42:01.936
<i>[overlapping angry shouts]</i>

42:03.938 --> 42:05.189
<i>[panting]</i>

42:05.272 --> 42:06.148
<i>Hit me again.</i>

42:07.691 --> 42:08.901
<i>[grunting]</i>

42:08.984 --> 42:10.444
<i>Again! Hit me!</i>

42:10.986 --> 42:12.571
<i>Luther, are you crazy? Just hit him!</i>

42:12.655 --> 42:13.739
<i>Come on, Luther!</i>

42:14.114 --> 42:15.741
<i>Hit me. I wanna feel pain.</i>

42:16.325 --> 42:17.868
<i>I wanna feel all the pain.</i>

42:20.704 --> 42:22.164
<i>Give me everything you've got!</i>

42:22.790 --> 42:23.874
<i>[growling]</i>

42:24.333 --> 42:26.335
<i>[crowd grows quiet]</i>

42:38.305 --> 42:40.766
<i>[crowd shouting]</i>

42:40.849 --> 42:43.435
<i>[overlapping boos]</i>

42:43.519 --> 42:45.521
<i>[angry shouts]</i>

42:47.898 --> 42:48.899
<i>Get outta my way.</i>

42:49.817 --> 42:50.859
<i>Shit.</i>

42:51.527 --> 42:53.779
<i>-Luther.</i>
<i>-[Vanya] Why didn't he fight back?</i>

42:53.862 --> 42:56.574
<i>[melancholy piano melody plays]</i>

42:57.950 --> 42:59.910
<i>[crowd sounds fading]</i>

43:11.714 --> 43:13.716
<i>[The Stranglers' "Golden Brown" plays]</i>

43:32.610 --> 43:35.946
<i>♪ </i>Golden Brown, texture like sun<i> ♪</i>

43:36.488 --> 43:39.908
<i>♪ Lays me down, with my mind she runs ♪</i>

43:39.992 --> 43:43.537
<i>♪ Throughout the night, no need to fight ♪</i>

43:43.912 --> 43:47.666
<i>♪ Never a frown with Golden Brown ♪</i>

43:51.920 --> 43:55.215
<i>♪ Every time, just like the last ♪</i>

43:55.758 --> 43:58.927
<i>♪ On her ship, tied to the mast ♪</i>

43:59.345 --> 44:03.057
<i>♪ To distant lands, takes both my hands ♪</i>

44:03.140 --> 44:06.894
<i>♪ Never a frown with Golden Brown ♪</i>

44:06.977 --> 44:08.228
<i>[puppy barks]</i>

44:08.312 --> 44:09.688
<i>[Lila] Hi, little guy.</i>

